A '''honeycomb''' is a [[food]] found in the [[Dungeon]] which provides 2,000 [[nutrition]] and can be eaten by any [[species]] at any level of hunger except engorged. Light-weight and filling, they are one of the finest foodstuffs.

It is rare to find them randomly generated, but cracking open any [[killer bee]] [[vault]]s you come across should reveal several honeycombs, along with [[royal jelly (item)|royal jelly]].

==History==
Honeycombs were renamed to royal jellies in [[0.15]]. The item formerly known as royal jelly was retired.

